{
  "texts": [
    "Firstly, the study was retrospective in nature and the radiographs did not include clinical information, which resulted in a lack of important parameters such as pain localisation [28].",
    "Secondly, the training data for Chat-GPT 4 is unknown to us.",
    "We cannot comment on the size of the dataset that the model was trained on.",
    "However, deep learning models perform worse when applied to new data sets and different patients [29].",
    "Therefore, our setting for ChatGPT 4 was more difficult, as the offered scenario of fracture images was not available for training."
  ]
}